    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2013 Ford Mustang Boss 302 Laguna Seca. At its heart lies the high-output 5.0L 'Road Runner' V8, featuring a forged rotating assembly and CNC-ported heads, mated to a close-ratio MT-82 6-speed manual transmission. This example retains its factory-spec 3.73 Torsen helical limited-slip differential and five-way manually adjustable dampers, providing surgical precision during high-G cornering. The braking system is anchored by Brembo four-piston calipers over 14-inch vented rotors, showing zero fade or glazing. Aerodynamics are bolstered by the aggressive front splitter and rear spoiler, while the cabin remains pristine with Alcantara touchpoints and the signature rear-seat delete X-brace for enhanced torsional rigidity. Mechanically flawless with no fluid seepage or bushing fatigue; a superlative example of track-bred engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
